Ebola Hemorrhagic Fever In Uganda - Who Update 25
--------------------------------------------------
As of Fri 10 Nov 2000, the Ugandan Ministry of Health has reported
cumulative figures for Gulu district of 301 cases of Ebola hemorrhagic
fever, including 99 deaths. [This represents an increase of 6 cases and 3
deaths during the past 24 hours. - Mod.CP
Of the three laboratory confirmed cases in Mbarara district, the 2 most
recently diagnosed cases have died.
--
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[The 24 hour case notifications for Gulu district over the past 5 days have
averaged approximately 4 cases (1, 3, 2, 9, & 6) and 2 deaths (2, 0, 3 ,2,
& 3). These figures suggest that the outbreak is being contained. - Mod.CP
